description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at what appears to be "The Dead Internet Theory" and how it's not a theory but objective fact as Internet traffic is slowly shifting from primarily human traffic to completely automated in a disturbing trend that could send the Internet into critical mass. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: The Internet Is Slowly Dying.. And We're Killing It...
